        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.5: \" Localization of the PMES-2 protein in a subcellular fraction\"\n- \"The immunoreactivity for the PMES-2 was detected in forebrain homogenate, synaptosome fraction, Triton-solubilized fraction (the supernatant of the fourth centrifuge) and PSD fraction at 42 kDa (Fig. 5B). \"\n\n23/3/2018 Pim\n- The WB looks so shady (could not reliably identify the PSD lane) that I did not annotate to PSD.. Experimental description: - \"The forebrains of 3-week-old Sprague-Dawley rats under anesthesia were dissected...\"" ;
